    <values>
        <field>Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">A live Experience Cloud network has AllowMembersToSeeEachOther=true. This allows guest users to enumerate other community members, their profiles, and potentially contact details.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Impact__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Community members can enumerate other members profiles and contact details. This enables targeted phishing, social engineering, and violates user privacy expectations.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Disable Allow guest users to see other members on each Experience network in Setup &gt; Digital Experiences &gt; [Site] &gt; Administration &gt; Members.</value>
